* Empower Fire (lv X): Increases party Fire damage dealt by X%
* Empower Ice (lv X): Increases party Ice damage dealt by X%
* Empower Lightning (lv X): Increases party Lightning damage dealt by X%
* Empower Earth (lv X): Increases party Earth damage dealt by X%
* Empower Wind (lv X): Increases party Wind damage dealt by X%
* Empower Water (lv X): Increases party Water damage dealt by X%
* Empower Holy (lv X): Increases party Holy damage dealt by X%
* Empower Dark (lv X): Increases party Dark damage dealt by X%
* Dampen Fire (lv X): Reduces party Fire damage taken by X%
* Dampen Blizzard (lv X): Reduces party Ice damage taken by X%
* Dampen Lightning (lv X): Reduces party Lightning damage taken by X%
* Dampen Earth (lv X): Reduces party Earth damage taken by X%
* Dampen Air (lv X): Reduces party Wind damage taken by X%
* Dampen Water (lv X): Reduces party Water damage taken by X%
* Dampen Light (lv X): Reduces party Holy damage taken by X%
* Dampen Dark (lv X): Reduces party Dark damage taken by X%
* Health Boon (lv X): Increases party max HP by X% of the magicites total max HP (100% main, 50% sub)
* Attack Boon (lv X): Increases party ATK by X% of the magicites total ATK (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Defense Boon (lv X): Increases party DEF by X% of the magicites total DEF (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Magic Boon (lv X): Increases party MAG by X% of the magicites total MAG (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Resistance Boon (lv X): Increases party RES by X% of the magicites total RES (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Mind Boon (lv X): Increases party MND by X% of the magicites total MND (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Blade Ward (lv X): Reduces party physical damage taken from PHY or NAT attacks by X%
* Spell Ward (lv X): Reduces party magical damage taken from BLK, WHT, BLU, SUM or NAT attacks by X%
* Precise Strikes (lv X): Increases party critical chance by X% (additive with other critical chance modifiers)
* Deadly Strikes (lv X): Increases party critical damage by X% (additive with the default +50% and other critical damage modifiers)
* Fast Act (lv X): Increases party cast speed by X%
* Healing Boon (lv X): Increases all HP restored to the party by X%
* Healing Damper (lv X): Decreases all HP restored to the party by X%
* Hand of Vengeance (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X*(1-HP%)^3 percent, where HP% is the character's current HP rate
* Surging Power (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X*HP/10000 percent, where HP is the character's current amount of HP (max +X%, reached at 10000 HP)
* Damage Push (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X%, acting and taking damage grants 25% less SB points
